			title: "Beyond the Stargate"
			x: 0.0d
			y: 0.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["TS01000000000001"]
			description: ["The Dragon does not guard treasure. It maintains the dimensional seal between the End and the Void—a seal that, once broken, allows passage to the outer islands where End Cities drift in permanent exile. It was never going to end any other way."]
