		}
		{
			dependencies: ["TS01000000000002"]
			description: ["The Elytra are found in End Ships docked at the outer island city towers. They are the wings of something that no longer exists—the remnants of a civilization that predated even the Overworld. They were made to be worn. Wear them."]
