		{
			dependencies: ["TS01000000000002"]
			description: ["The Dragon Egg is not an egg. It is a dimensional anchor—the compressed residue of the Dragon's connection to the End. When the Dragon dies, this forms at the exit portal's apex. It serves no mechanical purpose. It is a trophy. Take it anyway."]
