		{
			dependencies: ["TS01000000000001"]
			description: ["The End Cities float in the Void on chains of Purpur and End Stone. Each hosts a Ship docked at its highest tower. The Ship holds the Elytra and a Dragon's Breath stockpile. Navigate to the outer islands via the exit portal gateway—the Cities are worth the travel."]
